#

Carrot Salad with Lemon Dressing

10 min
$5
130 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Salad

Tags:

SaladQuickHealthyFresh

Description

A refreshing and crunchy salad that brightens up any meal with a zesty lemon dressing!

Ingredients

  • carrots: 4 large, grated
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • honey: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • fresh parsley: 2 tablespoons, chopped (optional)
